OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FTwo teenage boys drowned in the River
OL,7,FTyne in Northumberland after one tried
OL,8,Fto save the other, an inquest has
OL,9,Fheard.
OL,11,FDavid Radut, 14, and Aras Rudzianskas,
OL,12,F13, got into difficulties in the water
OL,13,Fafter playing on a rope swing on a
OL,14,Fstretch of the river at Ovingham in
OL,15,FMay 2024.
OL,17,FAn inquest in Morpeth on Monday (6
OL,18,FJuly) heard from witnesses who tried
OL,19,Fto save the schoolboys.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
