OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783720150
OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Danielle Grant, of
OL,7,FNorthumbria Police, told the inquest
OL,8,Fthe two boys were part of a group of
OL,9,Fyoungsters seen on CCTV boarding a bus
OL,10,Ffrom Newcastle to Ovingham on 18 May.
OL,12,FShe told the court witnesses suggested
OL,13,Fthe two boys started swinging on a
OL,14,Frope swing over the river and back
OL,15,Fagain, shortly after arriving.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783720150
OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FThe court was told they did this twice
OL,7,Fsuccessfully, but, according to
OL,8,Fwitnesses, on David's second attempt
OL,9,Fhe let go of the rope and fell into
OL,10,Fdeeper water, struggling because he
OL,11,Fcould not swim.
OL,13,FWitnesses said Aras went into the
OL,14,Fwater to rescue David, but was pulled
OL,15,Fdown as David panicked.
OL,17,FThe court heard two other boys
OL,18,Fattempted to help, but David
OL,19,Fdisappeared under the water and Aras
OL,20,Fwas taken by the current.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
