PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783720150
OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FDet Sgt Grant told the court a very
OL,7,Fbig response of 36 officers, a support
OL,8,Fhelicopter and drones were launched
OL,9,Fafter a group of distraught teens
OL,10,Fwaved down help.
OL,12,FDespite questions from David's family
OL,13,Fover who was saving who, Det Sgt Grant
OL,14,Fsaid all the witnesses concurred it
OL,15,Fwas Aras who jumped in to save David.
OL,17,FWhen asked if there was any merit in
OL,18,FDavid being pushed into the water, she
OL,19,Fsaid there was "nothing to suggest he
OL,20,Fwas pushed, dared or forced" to go in.
OL,26,@{D@POU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
