PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783720150
OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FFiona Mathews, who was paddle boarding
OL,7,Fin the river, told the court some boys
OL,8,Fshouted asking if she had seen anyone
OL,9,Fin the water.
OL,11,FShe said she found Aras and somehow
OL,12,Fmanaged to get him on her paddle board
OL,13,Fto perform CPR.
OL,15,FShe told the court she was then guided
OL,16,Fthrough compressions by paramedics who
OL,17,Fhad arrived and managed to paddle him
OL,18,Fto shallower water where they took
OL,19,Fover.
OL,21,FAras died in hospital three days later.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
