PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1783720150
OL,3,CInquest hears boys drowned in River
OL,4,CTyne after one tried to save the other
OL,6,FPolice divers told the inquest David
OL,7,Fwas located 21 meters downstream from
OL,8,Fthe rope swing and was declared dead
OL,9,Fat the scene.
OL,11,FThe inquest is expected to look into
OL,12,Fwhat safety precautions and signage
OL,13,Fwere in place at the river.
OL,15,FThe inquest continues on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
